      <title>比特币挖矿难度创历史新高，利润率压力加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-mining-difficulty-hits-record-with-pressure-mounting-on-profit-margins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加密货币开采公司之间的竞争愈演愈烈，衡量比特币开采难度的行业指标攀升至历史新高。]]></description>
